    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really don't want to risk passing out in my sleep. if i check my sugar and it's in the normal range right now, wouldn't it make more sense to just skip the dose since there isn't any new food coming in to spike it? it seems way safer to just be conservative with it tonight.",
